fuzzing, including the global optimization of seed energy scheduling and\nthe escape of local optimal seed. Additionally, 24 real-world vulnerabilities\nwere discovered using UltraFuzz.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Sep 2020 00:30:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 5 Nov 2022 01:26:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-16"}
