d englacial\nfracturing sources as well as novel constraints on heterogeneous nature of the\nnoise field generated by subglacial water flow and on the link between crevasse\nproperties and englacial seismic velocities. We finally outline in which ways\nfurther work using this dataset could help tackle key remaining questions in\nthe field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Sep 2020 10:47:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-15"}
