we are not longer limited to one\nsingle interface; the set of the messages that could be sent to an object could\nbe enlarged, and so, we may consider that using them, we can dynamically change\nthe type of objects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Sep 2020 12:58:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-15"}
