production of a small amount of water (5 mg/cm2). The combined information from\nthermal neutron radiography and cell response characteristics explains the\nimportant influence of cell orientation on the performance of a fully passive\nair-breathing PEMFC for portable applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Sep 2020 13:42:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-15"}
